<bibRefCitation author="Sanborn, A. F. &amp; Heath, M. S." box="[1089,1374,1577,1603]" pageId="91" pageNumber="92" pagination="1 - 94" refId="ref108909" refString="Sanborn, A. F. &amp; Heath, M. S. (2014) The cicadas of Argentina with new records, a new genus and fifteen new species (Hemiptera: Cicadoidea: Cicadidae). Zootaxa, 3883 (1), 1 - 94. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 3883.1.1" type="journal article" year="2014">Sanborn and Heath 2014</bibRefCitation>
